-- Ukraine May Buy 10 Billion Cubic Meters of Europe Gas, Ria Says
-- B y   D a r y n a   K r a s n o l u t s k a
-- 2012-03-17T11:21:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-17/ukraine-may-buy-10-billion-cubic-meters-of-europe-gas-ria-says.html
Ukraine’s state-owned energy
company NAK Naftogaz Ukrainy is considering buying 10 billion
cubic meters of natural gas on the spot market in  Europe ,  Ria
Novosti  news agency reported, citing Chief Executive Officer
Yevhen Bakulin.  Bakulin said Ukraine can buy gas from Europe’s spot market
in summer without disrupting the transit of Russian gas to the
European Union, according to Ria.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Daryna Krasnolutska in Kiev at 
